Detailed Description

A proxy between Europa domains and TREX domains.

This class acts as a proxy in order to make europa Domain instances easily accessible for TREX. It behave as a tempraray proxy that llow TREX to access to a domain information without necessary requireing to convert this domain into its TREX counterpart. The copy of an instance of this class will do the conversion of the europa domain into a its TREX domain representation.

Note:
This lcass is really meant to be used as a temporary proxy to ease the whole europa to trex conversion process. It is not really meant for a more classic trex domain usage and we do recommend to copy a EuropaProxy before doing many extra manipulation.
Bug:
Many of the methods here are actually doinfg the domain conversion under the hood and it may be worthwhile to cache such conversion instead of doing it every time one of these call is made.
Author:
Frederic Py <fpy@mbari.org>

void DomainBase::accept ( DomainVisitor &  visitor  )  const [virtual, inherited]

Visiting method.

Parameters:
visitor A domain visitor

This method implement the Visitor design pattern for TREX domains. It will call visitor methods depending on the actual type of this instance.

There's 3 possible cases supported :

  • this class is a BasicInterval instance
  • this class is a BasicEnumerated instance
  • this class is none of the above

in each case the corresponding method of visitor will be called

See also:
DomainVisitor

template<class Ty , bool Safe>
Ty TREX::transaction::DomainBase::getTypedSingleton (  )  const [inline, inherited]

singleton value

Template Parameters:
Ty output type
Safe robust conversion

This methods give acces to the value of a singleton instance The output will be of type Ty

The Safe parameter indicates which method should be used.

  • If the real type of the underneath domain type is guaranteed to be Ty the Safe can be false for performance
  • If the type is not guaranteed to be Ty but its text representation is compatible with Ty the Safe should be true
Precondition:
the instance is a singleton
the type of the value manip[ulated by this domain should be convertible to Ty or exactly Ty is Safe is false
Exceptions:
DomainAccess the insatnce was not a singleton
boost::bad_string_cast Safe is true and the value of the singleton cannot be parse into Ty
boost::bad_string_cast Safe is false and the type of the singleton is not Ty
Returns:
The singleton value of this domain
